               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalota ʿǝṭan “Prayer of Incense” (fols. 5ra-87vb)&#xD; - Prayer of
                     Incense for Sunday (za-ba-ʾǝḥud) (fols. 57va-81va)&#xD; - Prayer of
                     Thanksgiving (ṣalota ʾakkʷatet) (fols. 82ra-87vb)&#xD; &#xD;
                     Colophon.</summary>
